text.section:
Each county board shall hold an annual meeting on or as near as possible to the second Tuesday in July, except that:
In Allegany County, the annual meeting shall be held on the second Tuesday in January;
In Montgomery County, the annual meeting shall be held on or before January 10;
In Prince George's County, the annual meeting shall be held on the first Monday in December;
In St. Mary's County, the annual meeting shall be held following the first Monday in December; and
In Washington County, the annual meeting shall be held in December, on or before the 16th day.
